attributes.spec_overview:
KTM 390 Duke Bike is one of India’s most reputed 2-wheelers. The 390 Duke Bike is manufactured by KTM, popularly known for their technologically advanced manufacturing value. KTM 390 Duke Bike belongs to the Bike category. The Bike boasts high-tech specifications like 373.2 CC engine that produces 32 kW @ 9000 rpm power, 28.9 Kmpl mileage and giving the most superior driving experience to its users. KTM 390 Duke Bike is the kind of 2-wheeler that will turn heads wherever it’s driven.

KTM 390 Duke Price In India

KTM 390 Duke Price in India starts from ₹ 2.96 Lakh. BikeJunction provides you a complete list of the updated and accurate price range of KTM 390 Duke Bike. However, it is necessary to know that the on-road price of the 390 Duke Bike may differ from state to state, depending upon their specific government taxation policies.

KTM 390 Duke Engine

KTM 390 Duke engine capacity is 373.2 CC and engineered with Single Cylinder, Liquid Cooled, DOHC, FI Engine engine. This engine generates 32 kW @ 9000 rpm and 37 Nm @ 7000 rpm of Torque. The engine of 390 Duke is aligned with a 6 Speed gear transmission.

KTM 390 Duke Mileage

KTM 390 Duke mileage is 28.9 Kmpl which is very adequate. The Bike comes with a fuel tank capacity of 13.4 L litres. This combination gives this Bike a good driving range.

KTM 390 Duke Brakes & Suspension

KTM 390 Duke comes with the top-of-the-line enhanced and powerful braking system. In addition, the 2-wheeler has powerful and strong brakes, giving maximum control to its users. The suspension system of the 390 Duke Bike is also very impressive that ensures smoother drive experience while enabling the Bike to negotiate through rough terrains.

KTM 390 Duke at BikeJunction is available with complete information. In addition you can easily get the KTM 390 Duke on-road price in India. BikeJunction also provides you a smart comparison tool that will let you comprehensively compare the KTM 390 Duke Bike with your other top choices.
